snippet.title: Sushi Cat 2: The Great Purrade
snippet.description: Sushi Cat 2: The Great Purrade Arcade game. Feed the cat the targetted amount of sushi's each of the levels.

snippet.title: Ice Cream Catapult
snippet.description: Ice Cream Catapult Skill game. Use the icecreams and a big catapult to destroy the enemy's base and units.

snippet.title: Catnarok Longcat Rampage
snippet.description: Catnarok Longcat Rampage Use your eyebeams to destroy the in- coming units. Survive as long as you can.

snippet.title: Catch The Candy: Halloween
snippet.description: Catch The Candy: Halloween Puzzle game. Your sticky tongue skills make sure you can reach the candy.

snippet.title: Cat-a-Pult
snippet.description: Cat-a-Pult Hit the cats through the holes in the wall using your catapult. Not suitable for cat lovers...

snippet.title: Cat-Vac
snippet.description: Cat-Vac You must once again rid the Medieval Castle of the cats. This time you are armed with a Cat-Vac.

snippet.title: Crazy Penguin Catapult
snippet.description: Crazy Penguin Catapult Polar bears have captured your friends. Use the catapult to help them escape.

snippet.title: Sushi Cat
snippet.description: Sushi Cat Guide the Sushi Cat to as much sushi as possible and watch him grow fat. Fill his belly to win a level.

snippet.title: Zombie Cats
snippet.description: Zombie Cats Help the dog to save the city from zombie cats. Use your mouse to cause actions that help you kill them.

snippet.title: Catch the Bones
snippet.description: Catch the Bones Physics puzzle. Try to collect bones using a dog that you can inflate and deflate to get them all.
